    Modi
    Personal Mobility Device
    2024


    Urban Freedom, Right at your Feet

    We aim to address the transportation issues faced by modern city dwellers.
    In complex and congested urban areas, PMD (Personal Mobility Device) is highly useful.
    However, many PMD have become a new nuisance on the roads due to their heavy weight, large size,
    and disorderly presence.

    To solve these problems, we designed Modi.
    Modi is compact enough to fit in a backpack and lightweight for easy portability.
    These features make urban life simpler and more convenient for users.

    Take a break with your feet, thanks to Modi.


    Conventional PMD is large and heavy, making them difficult to carry.
    Additionally, users often face parking issues after reaching their destination.


    Permalink
    Permalink
    Permalink
    Automatic Pop-up Footrests.


    Permalink
    Permalink
    Permalink
    Permalink
    Permalink


    < Our Role >

    We have focused our research on providing a PMD that is easily portable without parking or storage issues.
    We achieved this through a compact design,
    emphasizing small size and exceptional maneuverability as key features.


    Permalink
    Permalink


    The footrests, hidden when not in use, securely hold your feet in place during drive, providing stability.
    When not in use, the footrests fold away, allowing for more compact storage,
    making it easier to carry in tight spaces like at home or in the office.
